91
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,320
In other words,

92
00:04:34,770 --> 00:04:36,560
it's okay to read

93
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,850
the negative comments online,

94
00:04:37,850 --> 00:04:38,850
but don't overthink it.

95
00:04:39,050 --> 00:04:40,000
Fame brings you trouble.

96
