Now you're a world champion,

97
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,280
- Exactly.
- right?

98
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,530
Master, Mrs. Fang, I got it.

99
00:04:44,530 --> 00:04:45,610
I was freaked out.

100
00:04:45,650 --> 00:04:46,880
I was wondering what happened.

101
00:04:46,970 --> 00:04:47,810
Don't worry.

102
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,010
I read the post.

103
00:04:49,020 --> 00:04:49,950
It's just nonsense.

104
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:51,880
I won't take it seriously.

105
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,880
I'm a tough girl now.

106
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:54,880
Don't worry.

107
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:56,000
I know how hard

108
