119
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:18,730
Don't overthink it.

120
00:05:18,730 --> 00:05:19,650
Stay true to yourself.

121
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,440
Enjoy the food. Bye.

122
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,280
Bye.

123
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,240
Master, Mrs. Fang, bye.

124
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,160
Lin Ge.

125
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,760
Are you really fine?

126
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,580
Why would I be upset?

127
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:35,710
It's just a post.

128
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:38,770
Maybe I learned to be rational

129
00:05:38,770 --> 00:05:39,680
from someone.

130
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:43,320
I only want the people who I care about
to believe me

131
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,120
and recognize my ability.

132
00:05:45,610 --> 00:05:46,730
Nothing else matters.

133
00:05:58,410 --> 00:05:59,730
What are they talking about?

134
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,880
What's wrong with them?

135
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:06,290
Lin Ge.

136
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,610
I want to apologize.

137
00:06:08,730 --> 00:06:09,680
For what?

138
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,050
I saw the post online.

139
00:06:12,410 --> 00:06:13,320
Sorry, you were

140
00:06:13,650 --> 00:06:14,680
slandered because of me.

141
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:15,850
It's okay.

142
00:06:15,850 --> 00:06:16,920
They're talking nonsense.

143
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,300
I don't care what they think.

144
00:06:19,210 --> 00:06:20,050
However, Wei,

145
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,770
I do need to tell you something.

146
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:24,050
