150
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,050
Do you hate me?

151
00:06:34,050 --> 00:06:35,320
You don't want to play with me?

152
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,770
- No.
- Then why did you say that?

153
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:40,090
I just want you to learn

154
00:06:40,090 --> 00:06:41,050
