I won't bother you anymore.

164
00:06:55,970 --> 00:06:57,440
Please don't hate me.

165
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:59,120
Don't be angry, okay?

166
00:07:02,770 --> 00:07:05,320
I'm not angry, and I don't hate you.

167
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,440
I'm not upset either.

168
00:07:06,850 --> 00:07:08,850
However, my energy is limited.

169
00:07:09,090 --> 00:07:12,240
I also want to get up late,
do the laundry, and do my own stuff

170
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,290
