174
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,720
I got it.

175
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,210
As for tomorrow's event,

176
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,090
I'll go with Gao Kai.

177
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:25,960
I swear,

178
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,480
I won't force you to come anymore.

179
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,400
Okay.

180
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,210
I'm so glad you can

181
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:43,560
understand me.

182
