187
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,560
He even expressed his love on Weibo.

188
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:04,560
But she ignored him.

189
00:08:08,410 --> 00:08:09,850
Bad news. Check the Super Topic

190
00:08:09,850 --> 00:08:11,090
of Kai or Wei.

191
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,280
Super Topic?

192
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,160
Yes.

193
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:16,300
(Gao Kai)

194
00:08:18,150 --> 00:08:18,990
Oh my god.

195
00:08:21,610 --> 00:08:22,450
What?

196
