206
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:56,900
I can't guarantee that.

207
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:59,250
It depends on his recovery progress.

208
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,520
Coach.

209
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,720
Was the show fun?

210
00:09:15,170 --> 00:09:17,050
Now you're injured.
You know it's serious.

211
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,130
