Li.

220
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,440
Don't try to defend him.

221
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:39,130
I will keep my promise.

222
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:43,890
Sorry, doctor.

223
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,160
It's okay?

224
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,530
Stop standing here.

225
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,680
Follow me.

226
00:09:51,010 --> 00:09:54,080
Doctor, look at this.

227
00:10:01,130 --> 00:10:04,320
Coach, that was so real.

228
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,770
It doesn't matter,

229
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:10,370
as long as my message

230
00:10:10,890 --> 00:10:11,920
can be delivered.

231
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:14,970
I knew it.

232
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,280
You knew what?

233
00:10:17,290 --> 00:10:20,320
Torn ligament and hairline fracture
are not a big deal,

234
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,680
but you have to rest well,

235
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,560
understand?

236
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,640
Yes.

237
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:27,010
You yelled at me on purpose

238
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,050
because you wanted

239
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:30,560
to stop them from inviting me
to these events, right?

240
00:10:31,290 --> 00:10:32,130
Listen,

241
00:10:32,290 --> 00:10:34,410
an athlete needs good results.

242
00:10:34,490 --> 00:10:37,680
Only good results
can lead you to success.

243
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:40,250
Other things are just illusions.

244
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,680
Got it.

245
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:42,760
Thanks, coach.

246
00:10:45,490 --> 00:10:46,330
Remember

247
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,720
to take some pictures of your foot.

248
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,400
Why?

249
00:10:53,050 --> 00:10:55,890
World champion,
don't you have a Weibo account?

250
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,010
Do I need to teach you?

251
00:10:58,290 --> 00:10:59,130
So dumb.

252
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,680
Cunning old fox.

253
00:11:06,650 --> 00:11:08,130
What happened?

254
00:11:08,170 --> 00:11:09,290
Can he walk?

255
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,530
Why are you shaking your head?

256
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:15,050
Can he walk or not?

257
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,520
Jinting,

258
00:11:16,770 --> 00:11:18,890
