262
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,920
Jinting, Jinting.

263
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,130
Take it easy. Don't push her.

264
00:11:27,130 --> 00:11:28,650
Yes, Jinting, don't push her.

265
00:11:28,650 --> 00:11:29,800
- She was freaked out.
- Shut up!

266
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,720
